      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――収録終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1400.0000516999999,
          "startTime": 1.4000000517
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 52372.5857735,
          "startTime": 52.3725857735
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 105131.5907638,
          "startTime": 105.1315907638
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 155173.972714,
          "startTime": 155.173972714
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1400.0000516999999,
          "startTime": 1.4000000517
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……や、やっとここまで来れた……\nすっかり暗くなっちゃったな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、まだ待ってくれてたりするのかな……\n寒いし、どこか暖かい場所にいてほしいけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4721766524,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11836.5663104,
          "startTime": 26.3087429628
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "あそこにいるの……もしかして、雫ちゃん！？\nまだ、私のこと……っ……雫ちゃーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4297001753,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5204.722480600001,
          "startTime": 28.6344226559
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、千紗ちゃん。遅くまで、お仕事お疲れ様\n収録、無事に終わった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.3666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "うん、待たせてごめんね……でも……良かった……\n返信がなかったから、何かあったのかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね。スマホのバッテリーが切れちゃって\n行き違いになるのも悪いから、海を眺めてた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.4333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんだ……先に帰ってても良かったのに\n私のせいで寒い思いをさせちゃったよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "じっと待つのは釣りで慣れてるから大丈夫\n待った甲斐があって、とびきり可愛い大物が釣れた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.2666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "そうなの？　どこにいるんだろう……\nあれ、釣りの道具、持ってきてないよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで。それに待ってたのは、千紗ちゃんに\n「お疲れ様」って伝えたかったのもあったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.0666670482,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7933.332951799997,
          "startTime": 93
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん。お仕事お疲れ様。これ、差し入れのココア\nもう、冷めちゃってるかもだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0000003815,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8818.66101179999,
          "startTime": 97.46
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "っ、本当だ……こんなに冷たくなってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.865309624,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "ち、千紗ちゃん。それ、ココアっていうか私の手……\n冷えちゃうから、離した方が……千紗ちゃん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9739474115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね、私、待たせてばっかりで……時間もあんまり\n作れなくて……っ……せっかく選んでくれたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1723157746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.629912746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、雫ちゃん。メンバーは、サニピの中なら\n選べるんだよね？　なら、今からでも他の――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3000034333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんがいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.9463134726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "え……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.4408888619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "私は、千紗ちゃんと作りたい。千紗ちゃんと歌いたい\nゆっくりでいいし、迷惑だなんて思わない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.6333316804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "今までだって、遅いって思われても、道が遠くても……\n隣に千紗ちゃんがいたから、私は頑張れた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.1666650137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "だから……一緒に歌おう？\n私達なりに、私達のペースで。一緒に頑張ろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.6999983471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん……っ、うん、私も雫ちゃんがいい\n雫ちゃんと一緒に歌いたい。歌と想いを、届けたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.0333316804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。私、口下手だけど、大丈夫？\nたぶん歌詞も、沢山悩んじゃう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.3333316804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だよ。そういうところも全部含めて\n雫ちゃんは、私の――一番の親友だもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.8333316804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "っ、千紗ちゃん……。うん、そうだね……\n私にとっても、千紗ちゃんは――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.9903315791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.7540597757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 216.074053677
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 216.1540587585
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_03-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "なんとか新曲、完成したけど\nすぐにMV撮影だなんて、目が回りそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.0225768612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 224.1140608311
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
